<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>RunwaySync - Contraseña Restablecida</title>
  <style>
    *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
    html,body{width:100%;height:100%;overflow:hidden;}
    body{background:#ffffff;}
    .page{
      position:relative;
      width:100vw;
      height:100vh;
      overflow:hidden;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
    }
    .bg-svg{
      position:absolute;
      top:0;left:0;
      width:100%;
      height:100%;
      object-fit:fill;
      z-index:1;
    }
    .card-overlay{
      position:relative;
      z-index:10;
      background:#d9d9d9;
      border-radius:22px;
      width:448px;
      padding:40px 46px 34px;
      box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      text-align:center;
    }
    .check-circle{
      width:72px;
      height:72px;
      background:#141516;
      border-radius:50%;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      margin:0 auto 22px;
      animation: popIn 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175,0.885,0.32,1.275);
    }
    @keyframes popIn{
      from{transform:scale(0);opacity:0;}
      to{transform:scale(1);opacity:1;}
    }
    .check-circle svg{
      width:34px;
      height:34px;
      stroke:#ffffff;
      fill:none;
      stroke-width:2.5;
      stroke-linecap:round;
      stroke-linejoin:round;
    }
    .card-title{
      font-family:'Georgia',serif;
      font-size:2rem;
      font-weight:700;
      color:#141516;
      margin-bottom:10px;
      letter-spacing:0.01em;
    }
    .card-subtitle{
      font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;
      font-size:0.85rem;
      color:#6f6f6f;
      margin-bottom:32px;
      line-height:1.6;
    }
    .btn-main{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      width:100%;
      height:52px;
      background:#141516;
      color:#ffffff;
      font-family:'Georgia',serif;
      font-size:1.05rem;
      font-weight:700;
      text-decoration:none;
      border:none;
      cursor:pointer;
      border-radius:50px;
      letter-spacing:0.02em;
      box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);
      transition:background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    }
    .btn-main:hover{background:#333;transform:translateY(-1px);}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
  <img class="bg-svg" src="/svg/9.svg" alt=""/>
  <div class="card-overlay">
    <div class="check-circle">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h2 class="card-title">¡Contraseña Restablecida!</h2>
    <p class="card-subtitle">Tu contraseña ha sido actualizada exitosamente.<br/>Ya puedes iniciar sesión con tu nueva contraseña.</p>
    <a href="/login" class="btn-main">Ir al Inicio de Sesión</a>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
